rows.label: qev086910_MSG0001
rows.name: I watched those beams come tumbling straight at me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086910_MSG0002
rows.name:
Would have crushed me to a paste if Rock hadn't been
there, and that's a fact.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086910_MSG0003
rows.name:
I could kiss that boy right on that invincible noggin
of his! I owe him my life.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086910_MSG0004
rows.name:
Soon as work starts back up, I'll teach him all those
Earth construction methods he was asking about.
It's the least I can do.[ST:wait ]
